cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.DS 

The paper presents a novel bio-inspired approach to clustering news articles using Second Order Swarm Intelligence algorithm based on Ant Colony Optimization. The algorithm uses a negative pheromone to mark unrewarding paths with a "no-entry" signal. The paper also presents a new similarity measure between documents based on the Q-analysis description of the simplicial complex formed between documents and keywords. This work falls under the categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Swarm Intelligence (cs.SI), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
